messages.message: Thanks for the analysis -- @Prashant Kikani @Varun Jain if you can put that second table per sheet new feature in a Jira ticket so we can keep track. Overall these are limitations that we should put into the docs so people konw. cc @Hari
From the model-dev side, we're tracking it here in this Jira ticket: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/DR-2969

Yes, we already have the table extraction limitations (https://aihub.instabase.com/docs/aihub/releasenotes/known-issues/index.html) (including the multiple tables in excel sheet) in the docs. We also have a EPD initiative (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-1278) tracking this need, but it will not be prioritised in Q1. We have a lot of other higher priority tickets for table improvements.
